{"id":36,"date":"2021-10-07T01:03:25","date_gmt":"2021-10-07T01:03:13","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/cagbcprod.wpengine.com\/?page_id=36"},"modified":"2023-12-21T07:23:09","modified_gmt":"2023-12-21T12:23:09","slug":"building-climate-solutions","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/why-green-building\/building-climate-solutions\/","title":{"rendered":"Building climate solutions"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-top:0px\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>A proven path to lower carbon emissions<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The growing impact of climate change demands action, and buildings must be part of the solution. Slowing the rise in global temperatures means cutting carbon emissions. Today, residential, commercial, and institutional buildings contribute 17% of Canada&#8217;s greenhouse gas (GHG) emissions. Considering building materials and construction brings that number is closer to 30%, making the building sector Canada&#8217;s third-highest carbon emitter.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Green buildings offer a proven solution. They are more energy and resource efficient, use renewable energy, and work with the environment around them. Zero-carbon buildings help lower carbon emissions by addressing embodied carbon from construction materials and processes and from heating, cooling, and refrigerant use. Committing to green, zero-carbon buildings and deep carbon retrofits will reduce carbon emissions, helping slow rising global temperatures.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>CAGBC plays an active role in making zero-carbon buildings the new normal through&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/our-work\/research\/\">research<\/a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/learn\/\">education<\/a>, and the&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/our-work\/certification\/zero-carbon-building-standard\/\">Zero Carbon Building standards<\/a>.\u2122<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull is-light\" style=\"min-height:326px\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-0 has-background-dim\"><\/span><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2560\" height=\"850\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-3478\" alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/gbb_phenix_fullwidth_2560x850.jpg\" style=\"object-position:69% 12%\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" data-object-position=\"69% 12%\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/gbb_phenix_fullwidth_2560x850.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/gbb_phenix_fullwidth_2560x850-300x100.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/gbb_phenix_fullwidth_2560x850-1024x340.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/gbb_phenix_fullwidth_2560x850-768x255.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/gbb_phenix_fullwidth_2560x850-1536x510.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/gbb_phenix_fullwidth_2560x850-2048x680.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-large-font-size\"><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-tree-green-color has-text-color\" id=\"whats-a-zero-carbon-building\"><strong>What&#8217;s a zero carbon building?&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A zero-carbon building is highly energy-efficient and minimizes GHG emissions from building materials and operations. Until all emissions can be eliminated, high-quality carbon offsets can be used as a counterbalance.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-top:0\">\n    <div class=\"is-style-section-headline \">\n        <h2 class=\"has-h-4-font-size spacing-bottom-0\" id=\"h-case-studies-65b609dfa1377\">ZERO CARBON BUILDING SHOWCASE<\/h2>\n        <div class=\"wp-block-buttons\">\n            <div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-main is-style-main--small\">\n                <a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-tree-green-color\" aria-describedby=\"h-case-studies-65b609dfa1377\" href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/showcase\/green-building-spotlight\/?rtng=zero-carbon-building\">Read More<\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n                <div class=\"wp-custom-grid\">\n                                    <div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n                        <div class=\"wp-custom-card icon-wordmark-tree-green\">\n                            <div>\n                                \n                                <h3 class=\"wp-custom-card__title has-h-5-font-size spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/green-building-showcase\/green-building-spotlight\/case-studies\/co-operators-new-headquarters\/\">\n                                        Co-operators New Headquarters                                    <\/a>\n                                <\/h3>\n                                <div class=\"has-h-6-font-size has-charcoal-grey-color spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    The new Co-operators headquarters building located at 101 Cooper Drive, Guelph, aims to&hellip;                                <\/div>\n                                <span class=\"has-h-7-font-size has-medium-grey-color spacing-top-auto\">\n                                    June 16, 2023                                <\/span>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                                    <div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n                        <div class=\"wp-custom-card icon-wordmark-tree-green\">\n                            <div>\n                                \n                                <h3 class=\"wp-custom-card__title has-h-5-font-size spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/green-building-showcase\/green-building-spotlight\/case-studies\/edifice-jacques-parizeaus-zcb-performance\/\">\n                                        \u00c9difice Jacques-Parizeau                                    <\/a>\n                                <\/h3>\n                                <div class=\"has-h-6-font-size has-charcoal-grey-color spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    ZCB-Performance certification to guide future Ivanho\u00e9 Cambridge projects Located in Montreal\u2019s International District,&hellip;                                <\/div>\n                                <span class=\"has-h-7-font-size has-medium-grey-color spacing-top-auto\">\n                                    April 28, 2022                                <\/span>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                                    <div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n                        <div class=\"wp-custom-card icon-wordmark-tree-green\">\n                            <div>\n                                \n                                <h3 class=\"wp-custom-card__title has-h-5-font-size spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/green-building-showcase\/green-building-spotlight\/case-studies\/scotia-plazas-40-king-street-west\/\">\n                                        Scotia Plaza\u2019s 40 King Street West                                    <\/a>\n                                <\/h3>\n                                <div class=\"has-h-6-font-size has-charcoal-grey-color spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    Zero carbon building reaches new heights with first ZCB-Performance v2 certification Scotia Plaza\u2019s&hellip;                                <\/div>\n                                <span class=\"has-h-7-font-size has-medium-grey-color spacing-top-auto\">\n                                    April 28, 2022                                <\/span>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                                    <div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n                        <div class=\"wp-custom-card icon-wordmark-tree-green\">\n                            <div>\n                                \n                                <h3 class=\"wp-custom-card__title has-h-5-font-size spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/green-building-showcase\/green-building-spotlight\/case-studies\/the-phenix\/\">\n                                        The Phenix                                    <\/a>\n                                <\/h3>\n                                <div class=\"has-h-6-font-size has-charcoal-grey-color spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    Phenix rises again with Zero Carbon Building-certified retrofit Architecture, planning and design firm&hellip;                                <\/div>\n                                <span class=\"has-h-7-font-size has-medium-grey-color spacing-top-auto\">\n                                    April 28, 2022                                <\/span>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                \n            <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull is-light is-style-banner-ads\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-moss-green-background-color has-background-dim-100 has-background-dim\"><\/span><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-1604\" alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/banner-ad-become-a-member-scaled.webp\" style=\"object-position:86% 36%\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" data-object-position=\"86% 36%\"\/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-cloud-white-color has-text-color has-h-9-font-size\">Looking for COVID information?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button aligncenter\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-cloud-white-color has-text-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/news-resources\/technical-documents\/leed-arc-covid-19-faqs\/covid-information-for-projects\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">learn more<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-bottom:0\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-tree-green-color has-text-color\" id=\"climate-priority\"><strong>Climate priority<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>To slow global warming and avoid the worst impacts of climate change, energy efficiency must go up, and carbon emissions must come down. Zero-carbon buildings offer a solution for both new construction and existing buildings, and can spur economic growth and new high-skilled jobs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading has-h-8-font-size\" id=\"making-the-case\"><strong>Making the Case&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>CAGBC&#8217;s report <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/news-resources\/research-and-reports\/making-the-case-for-zero-carbon-building\/\">Making the Case for Zero Carbon Buildings<\/a> proves zero-carbon buildings are technically feasible and financially viable. Investment in zero-carbon buildings protects against the rising cost of carbon and offers benefits beyond carbon reduction. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-main\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-tree-green-color has-text-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/news-resources\/research-and-reports\/making-the-case-for-zero-carbon-building\/\"><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Making the Case: <\/span>Read the report<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading has-h-8-font-size\"><strong>Decarbonizing Canada&#8217;s Large Buildings<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Existing buildings must be retrofit or renovated to be zero carbon if Canada is to meet its emissions reduction targets. CAGBC\u2019s study <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/news-resources\/research-and-reports\/decarbonizing-canadas-large-buildings\/\">Decarbonizing Canada&#8217;s Large Buildings<\/a><\/strong> examines how building owners can use deep carbon retrofits to accelerate the decarbonization of large buildings.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-main\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-tree-green-color has-text-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/portal.cagbc.org\/cagbcdocs\/advocacy\/2021_CaGBC_Decarbonization-Retrofit-Costing-Study_2DEC21_EN.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Read the summary<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">    <div class=\"is-style-section-headline \">\n        <h2 class=\"has-h-4-font-size\" id=\"h-research-reports\">LATEST RESEARCH &#038; REPORTS<\/h2>\n        <div class=\"wp-block-buttons\">\n            <div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-main is-style-main--small\">\n                <a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-tree-green-color\" aria-describedby=\"h-research-reports\" href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/news-insights\/research-and-reports\/\">MORE<\/a>    \n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n                <div class=\"wp-custom-grid\">\n                                    <div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n                        <div class=\"wp-custom-card icon-wordmark-tree-green\">\n                            <div>\n                                \n                                <h3 class=\"wp-custom-card__title has-h-5-font-size spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/fr\/news-resources\/research-and-reports\/divulgation-complete-2022\/\">\n                                        Divulgation compl\u00e8te : Le leadership climatique de l\u2019immobilier en action                                    <\/a>\n                                <\/h3>\n                                <div class=\"has-h-6-font-size has-charcoal-grey-color spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    En l\u2019absence d\u2019exigences et de soutien coh\u00e9rents en mati\u00e8re de divulgation des donn\u00e9es&hellip;                                <\/div>\n                                <span class=\"has-h-7-font-size has-medium-grey-color spacing-top-auto\">\n                                    October 26, 2022                                <\/span>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                                    <div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n                        <div class=\"wp-custom-card icon-wordmark-tree-green\">\n                            <div>\n                                \n                                <h3 class=\"wp-custom-card__title has-h-5-font-size spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/news-resources\/research-and-reports\/full-disclosure-2022-report\/\">\n                                        Full Disclosure: Real Estate&#8217;s Climate Leadership in action                                    <\/a>\n                                <\/h3>\n                                <div class=\"has-h-6-font-size has-charcoal-grey-color spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    In the absence of consistent requirements and support for building performance data disclosure&hellip;                                <\/div>\n                                <span class=\"has-h-7-font-size has-medium-grey-color spacing-top-auto\">\n                                    October 26, 2022                                <\/span>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                                    <div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n                        <div class=\"wp-custom-card icon-wordmark-tree-green\">\n                            <div>\n                                \n                                <h3 class=\"wp-custom-card__title has-h-5-font-size spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/fr\/news-resources\/research-and-reports\/classeur-de-la-norme-bcz-design-v3\/\">\n                                        Classeur de la Norme BCZ-Design v3                                    <\/a>\n                                <\/h3>\n                                <div class=\"has-h-6-font-size has-charcoal-grey-color spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    Classeur de la Norme BCZ-Design v3,                                <\/div>\n                                <span class=\"has-h-7-font-size has-medium-grey-color spacing-top-auto\">\n                                    June 21, 2022                                <\/span>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                                    <div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n                        <div class=\"wp-custom-card icon-wordmark-tree-green\">\n                            <div>\n                                \n                                <h3 class=\"wp-custom-card__title has-h-5-font-size spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/fr\/news-resources\/research-and-reports\/norme-du-bcz-design-v3\/\">\n                                        Norme du BCZ-Design v3                                    <\/a>\n                                <\/h3>\n                                <div class=\"has-h-6-font-size has-charcoal-grey-color spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    La Norme du b\u00e2timent \u00e0 carbone z\u00e9ro \u2013 Design oriente la conception des&hellip;                                <\/div>\n                                <span class=\"has-h-7-font-size has-medium-grey-color spacing-top-auto\">\n                                    June 21, 2022                                <\/span>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                \n            <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-tree-green-color has-text-color\" id=\"zero-carbon-building-jobs\">Zero carbon building jobs<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In the race to reduce carbon emissions and meet Canada&#8217;s climate targets, zero-carbon buildings and retrofits are an important strategy. Already, the federal government has mandated that all its owned or leased buildings should pursue zero carbon. As more building owners follow suit, demand for green building workers will grow.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The CAGBC report,&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/news-resources\/research-and-reports\/canadas-green-building-engine\/\">Canada&#8217;s Green Building Engine<\/a>&nbsp;estimates that direct green building jobs could number 1.5 million by 2030 if the government pursues a green recovery from the economic impacts of the COVID-19 pandemic. However, investments in workforce reskilling will be needed to meet the technical demands of zero-carbon buildings.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-main\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-tree-green-color has-text-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/news-resources\/research-and-reports\/canadas-green-building-engine\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Zero carbon building jobs: <\/span>Read the report<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-top:0px\">\n    <div class=\"is-style-section-headline \">\n        <h2 class=\"has-h-4-font-size spacing-bottom-0\" id=\"h-news-articles-65b609dfb4953\">LATEST NEWS <\/h2>\n        <div class=\"wp-block-buttons\">\n            <div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-main is-style-main--small\">\n                <a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-tree-green-color\" aria-describedby=\"h-news-articles-65b609dfb4953\" href=\"                    ?thm=zero-carbon\">Read More                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n                <div class=\"wp-custom-grid\">\n                                    <div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n                        <div class=\"wp-custom-card icon-wordmark-tree-green\">\n                            <div>\n                                \n                                <h3 class=\"wp-custom-card__title has-h-5-font-size spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/news-resources\/cagbc-news\/expanding-the-zcb-project-information-available-online\/\">\n                                        Expanding the ZCB project information available online                                    <\/a>\n                                <\/h3>\n                                <div class=\"has-h-6-font-size has-charcoal-grey-color spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    Over the comings months, CAGBC will be expanding the project information publicly available&hellip;                                <\/div>\n                                <span class=\"has-h-7-font-size has-medium-grey-color spacing-top-auto\">\n                                    January 10, 2024                                <\/span>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                                    <div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n                        <div class=\"wp-custom-card icon-wordmark-tree-green\">\n                            <div>\n                                \n                                <h3 class=\"wp-custom-card__title has-h-5-font-size spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/news-resources\/cagbc-news\/survey-findings-your-thoughts-about-the-upcoming-zcb-design-standard\/\">\n                                        Survey findings: Your thoughts on the upcoming ZCB-Design Standard                                    <\/a>\n                                <\/h3>\n                                <div class=\"has-h-6-font-size has-charcoal-grey-color spacing-bottom-2\">\n                                    Earlier this fall we asked you for ideas to inform the ongoing evolution&hellip;                                <\/div>\n                                <span class=\"has-h-7-font-size has-medium-grey-color spacing-top-auto\">\n                                    January 8, 2024                                <\/span>\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                                    <div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n                        <div class=\"wp-custom-card icon-wordmark-tree-green\">\n                            <div>\n                                \n                            